childAltar.hintText: 3 Spiritual Stones found in Hyrule...^$0Link's Pocket...^$1Fire Temple...^$2Deku Tree...^$oYe who may become a Hero...&The path to the future is open...

adultAltar.hintText: An awakening voice from the Sacred&Realm will call those destined to be&Sages, who dwell in the five temples.^$8Dodongo's Cavern...^$3Jabu-Jabu's Belly...^$4Spirit Temple...^$5Forest Temple...^$6Water Temple...^$7Shadow Temple...^$lThe awakened ones will await&for the Hero to find %gGreg%w.^$bAnd the %revil one%w's key will be&provided by Zelda once %r5&Spiritual Stones and Medallions%w&are retrieved.^$kTogether with the Hero of Time,&the awakened ones will return&the light of peace to the world...

ganonText: What about Zelda makes you think&she'd be a better ruler than I?^I saved Lon Lon Ranch,&fed the hungry,&and my castle floats.
ganonHintText: Ha ha ha... You'll never beat me&by reflecting my lightning bolts&and unleashing the arrows from&%rKakariko Village%w!^And even if you do, you'll never&find the legendary blade hidden in&%rFire Temple%w!
sheikText: I overheard Ganondorf say that he&misplaced the %yLight Arrows%w in&%rKakariko Village%w.^He also stole %gthe Master Sword%w&and hid it in %rFire Temple%w.
dampeText: Whoever reads this, please enter&%rHyrule Field%w. I will let you&have my stretching, shrinking&keepsake.^I'm waiting for you.&--Damp√©
